title: The Brkfst World Mint Decision
body:
The Mint Decisions

As it stands, we are looking into 3 options for where we could take the minting of Brkfst World. You will be able to find those below. Please read them carefully. We will be forming an official poll (or even a snapshot vote) to allow the entire Brkfst World community to vote on the path we will take.

Option 1: To Continue As Is

This option is the simplest one. As we continue to build on the initial short term Menu items (Coffee, Merch, DAO, etc.), we will keep minting open and do our weekly reveals every Sunday with the community.

Option 2: Leave Mint Open + Giveaways

This option adds a little more excitement to Option 1. We could end up reserve minting the final 1:1s, as well as a few new 1:1s or new rare trait sdnwchs (that we would create if this option is decided upon), and do weekly giveaways along with the weekly reveals. Basically, each Sunday, if you minted within the previous week and were part of the weekly reveal, you would be entered into the giveaway for a shot at receiving one of the 1:1s or rare trait sndwchs.

Option 3: Close Mint Until DAO and Brkfst World Coffee

Option 3 is an interesting one. Basically, what we would do, is in 1–2 weeks time, we would close mint. All current holders that have minted sndwchs would then become part of the OG category, receive a special role, as well as be the only ones able to receive the first batch of Brkfst World Coffee and OG Merch for free. While the minting is closed, the team would work tirelessly in the background to make sure the coffee brand and the DAO are stood up legally and properly to set Brkfst World up for success. Once Brkfst World Coffee and the DAO are nearing their time to go live, we would then open up minting again for anyone who would want to be a part of the official launch of the DAO.
